modName: UNP Minidresses Collection Conversion - UNPB BBP HDT-PE
summary: A conversion of UNP Minidresses Collection by Tiwa44 to UNPB / UNPB BBP HDT-PE with working weight slider.
descriptionHtml:
This is a conversion of [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/47376/?]UNP Minidresses Collection by Tiwa44[/url] to UNPB body with working weight slider. This is just mesh and weight changes for the UNPB body. It requires Tiwa44's original Minidresses mod to be installed first.

In this mod UNPB will have a Breast Jiggle version and a no Breast Jiggle version.

I will be adding converted meshes when I have them "done".

Added : Semitransparent Barkeeper and Chef Meshes and Textures in Optional file 
Added : Semitransparent Barkeeper and Chef Meshes and Textures in Optional file, Alternative setting if you want to go swimming in your clothing.
Note: The setting change make them look slightly different and behave differently with Racemenu overlays to the body. Test either to see which you like better.
Added : UNP Minidresses Collection - Standalone - UNPB Patch in Miscellaneous file 
Added : Tavern Wench outfit with no Jewelry in Optional file 

==================================================================================================================================
